properties.full_description: Summit classic collection features deluxe undercounter appliances designed to bring modern luxury into the home. The CL2R248 is a 24 In. wide two-drawer all-refrigerator fully constructed from stainless steel. The fully finished cabinet allows freestanding use, while the front-breathing cooling system enables built-in installation under counters. The drawers can be customized with overlay panels to match or accent existing cabinetry design. The stainless steel kickplates and sleek handles complete the look. Frost-free operation ensures minimum user maintenance inside the 3.4 Cu. Ft. interior. Two adjustable dividers make it easy to separate the drawer compartments into two or four zones to easily accommodate a variety of sizes. A sliding chrome basket offers added storage convenience, while the LED lighting makes it easy to view stored contents when loading or unloading both sections. Additional features ensure the unit is running at its best. These include a high temperature alarm and open drawer alarm. The digital thermostat makes it easy and intuitive to manage the interior temperature, while a temperature memory function helps to recover all settings in the event of power loss. This model also has a sabbath mode setting that disables certain electrical features during periods of religious observance. With its flexible design and user-friendly features, the CL2R248 is the ideal drawer refrigerator for home settings looking to add convenient luxury to the kitchen. To create a matching set, pair with our CL2F249 frost-free all-freezer.
